Standards-Version: 1.0.0
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/hyperledger/indy-sdk/
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/hyperledger/indy-sdk/


Package: libvdrtools
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl1.0.0, libsqlite0, libzmq5
Suggests: build-essential
Description: A library that facilitates building standards
compliant and interoperable solutions for self-sovereign
identity by abstracting the operations for interacting with
a verifiable data registry as defined by Hyperledger Aries.


